Our nappy wallets feature 2 internal pockets big enough for 2-3 nappies ( depending on size), wipes and bags.
They feature 2 different sized closure positions one specifically for when your nappy wallets is full and the other when it is empty.
That way your change items stay secure no matter how many nappies you have in their or have used

2nd Picture is to show open view it doen not depict fabrics used internallyin this wallet. Fabrics will match in contrast to the wallet you select.

name: Funky Fish strap Savers
description:
Our all new strap savers are the perfect addition to any carseat, pram, stroller, capsule, or highchair to stop scratchy, irritating harnesses and seatbelts.
They are padded with 100% cotton batting and fully reversible.
And they snap together with polyresin snaps so that sneaky toddlers cannot remove them.

name: Multi dot BLACK Grab n Go
description:
Our popular Grab n Go change mat nappy clutches fold out to contain a waterproof changemat and 2 storage pockets. Once folded use the handy pram strap to fasten to your pram, trolley or even handbag! Keep baby away from public use chagemats and be able to change them anywhere with this handy clutch.
Never use a nappy bag again!
Clutch measures 25 x 30cm closed
Internal fabrics will vary depending on availability.

name: Flutterby Clips~ 40mm Alligator clips
description:
These ever popular butterflies are a gorgeous addition to any hair clips collection. With a wide array of colours you'll be hooked.
They are all fixed to a fully lined 40mm alligator clip. 
If you would like these made into baby clips (35mm) please email us for a custom order at pumpkinsnitch@live.com.au
By as singles or as sets, these clips make perfect stocking filler or party favors.

name: Traffic Crayon Wallet
description:
Our Crayon wallets come filled with 8 non toxic crayons and a notepad. 
They are the perfect size to pop in your handbag and bring out when out at unexpected waits such as dr appoints, resturants and even in the car. 
All fabric is fully interfaced to create a sturdy wallet when in use.
 
Measuring 9.5 X 14.5cm when closed 
(approximately 35cm when opened)

name: Ladybug Big Bib
description:
Our big bibs live up to thier name measuring 30cm in length they ensure full coverage of even the messiest of meals.
Backed with super thick and absorbant polar fleece they are so soft against precious skin. Featuring snap fastners for closure.

name: care bear bliss BLUE big bib
description:
Our big bibs have been specifically designed for FULL coverage. they dont just cover to waist length they also cover shoulders for messy roaming hands. They are made of premium cottons and backed with super absorbant polar fleece. They now fasten with polyresin snaps for extra security!
**Big Bibs are an exclusive Pumpkin Snitch Pattern and are copywritted to Pumpkin Snitch Designs**
